<section id="adminarea-states">
<title>Hali</title>

<para>
Through the "States" link on the Admin page, you can manage the different
ticket states you want to use in the system (see figure below).
</para>

<para>
<figure>
    <title>State management</title>
<screenshot>
<graphic fileref="screenshots/administration/adminarea/admin-states.png"
scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%"></graphic></screenshot></figure>
</para>

<para>
Baada ya mpangilio wa kawaida, kuna hali zilizofafanuliwa:
</para>

<itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        imefungwa kwa mafanikio
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        imefungwa pasipo mafanikio
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        unganishwa
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        mpya
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        wazi
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        inasubiri kufunga kiotomatiki+
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        inasubiri kufunga kiotomatiki-
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        kikumbusho kinachosubiri
    </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
    <para>
        ondolewa
    </para>
  </listitem>
</itemizedlist>

